msgid "Backend Development"
msgstr "Backend Dasturlash"

msgid "Building backend systems for multi-page websites and web applications, including user registration, authentication, payment integrations, subscription systems, and analytics. Developing CRM, LMS, and admin panels for hotels, restaurants, schools, online stores, and blogs."
msgstr "Ko'p sahifali veb-saytlar va ilovalar uchun backend tizimlarini quramiz. Foydalanuvchi ro'yxatdan o'tishi, autentifikatsiya, to'lov integratsiyalari, obuna tizimlari va analitika. Mehmonxonalar, restoranlar, maktablar, onlayn do'konlar va bloglar uchun CRM, LMS va admin panellar."

msgid "Developing multifunctional Telegram bots for restaurants, fast-food chains, and educational centers with full payment system integration and advanced analytics. Building moderator bots, auto-posting tools, and scrapers that collect data from websites in seconds."
msgstr "Restoranlar, fast-food va o'quv markazlari uchun to'liq to'lov tizimi va analitika bilan Telegram botlar yaratamiz. Moderator botlar, avto-post vositalari va soniyalar ichida ma'lumot yig'uvchi scraperlar."

msgid "API Integrations"
msgstr "API Integratsiyalar"

msgid "Connecting third-party services, payment systems, and external APIs into seamless integrations."
msgstr "Uchinchi tomon xizmatlar, to'lov tizimlari va tashqi APIlarni ulash."

msgid "DevOps & Deployment"
msgstr "DevOps va Joylashtirish"

msgid "Containerizing apps with Docker, setting up Linux servers, Git workflows and CI/CD pipelines."
msgstr "Docker bilan konteynerlash, Linux serverlarini sozlash, Git workflow va CI/CD."

